---
import SectionHeading from '@components/ui/SectionHeading.astro';
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
  <SectionHeading title="About" number="02" />

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-16 items-start" data-animate>
    <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-4">
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        I'm a Full Stack Developer based in Argentina, specializing in building
        high-performance e-commerce experiences for global brands.
      </p>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        At{' '}
        <a href="https://www.innovategroup.agency/en" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent font-medium hover:underline">Innovate Group</a>, I work with Shopify Plus to deliver custom storefronts, complex integrations,
        and platform migrations for brands like Cole Haan, Puma, L'Occitane, and many more.
      </p>
      <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
        My focus is on writing clean, performant code that drives conversions and delivers
        exceptional user experiences. From custom Liquid themes to third-party service
        integrations, I enjoy solving complex e-commerce challenges.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-center">
      <div class="w-48 h-48 rounded-2xl bg-accent/5 border border-accent/15 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-20 h-20 text-accent/20" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
